title: League client won't open
body: When i just got into a ranked game, my client crashed and i tried to open it but nothing would open, not even the launch button but i think it's people who are with optus that cannot open?

replies.body: I'm with TPG and my client won't open either.

A lot of people can't connect, but most still can.

I'm with Optus and I can connect. Don't think it's an ISP issue.
